original_title: รัก ปี ลึก
overview: Ror is a seller who has an interest in antiques and used goods. He believes the items called "Deadstock" are very valuable. Has its own value and can make money. So that Ror devoted all his time to these items and without realizing he had ignored his relationship with "Ann". He does not understand love can not wait and need to always be maintained.
title: Deadstock
